{"parse":{"title":"Darkclaw Lobster","pageid":50709,"wikitext":{"*":"<onlyinclude>{{{{{tpl|tooltip}}}\n|mode={{{mode|}}}\n|arg={{{arg|}}}\n|icon=INV_Misc_Fish_14\n|stack=20\n|quality=Common\n|name=Darkclaw Lobster\n|charges=1\n|ilvl=55\n|level=45\n|effect=Use: Restores 1392 health over 30 sec.  Must remain seated while eating.\n|sell={{cost|||12}}\n}}</onlyinclude>\n\n'''Darkclaw Lobster''' can be caught with a [[Fishing]] [[Skill]] level as low as 1, but it is ideal to attempt this once you have reached about 275-300. The catch rate has been estimated at 35-40%.\n\n== Fished from ==\n* The shore of the [[Bay of Storms]] in [[Azshara]].\n* The shore of [[Misty Reed Strand]] in [[Swamp of Sorrows]].\n** Also from the waters inside the [[Sunken Temple]].\n** Also from the [[Pool of Tears]].\n* The shore of the [[Blasted Lands]].\n\n== Ingredient for ==\nThis item is used to make:\n* {{loot|Common|Lobster Stew}}\n\n== Can be placed in  ==\n* Advanced Refrigeration Unit\n* Lure Master Tackle Box\n* Portable Refrigerator\n\n== Achievements ==\n* {{achievement|The Oceanographer}}\n\n== External links ==\n<!-- Read http://www.wowwiki.com/WoWWiki:External_links before posting your links here.\nLinks that do not conform to the rules will be DELETED.\nRepeat violations may result in a BAN.\nHave a nice day. :) -->\n{{elinks-item|13888}}\n{{Elink|link=http://www.elsanglin.com/fish/darkclaw_lobster.html |site=El's Extreme Anglin' |icon=elsanglin}}\n[[Category:Fish]]\n[[Category:World of Warcraft common items]]\n[[Category:World of Warcraft cooking ingredient items]]\n[[Category:World of Warcraft food items]]"}}}